<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>400 • Curatorian</title>
    <link phx-track-static rel="stylesheet" href={~p"/assets/css/app.css"} />
    <style>
      /* Minimal fallback styles for error pages */
      html,body{height:100%}
      body{font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;margin:0;padding:2rem;background:#f5f3ff;color:#111}
      .max-w-3xl{max-width:48rem}
      .mx-auto{margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto}
      .px-4{padding-left:1rem;padding-right:1rem}
      .p-10{padding:2.5rem}
      .rounded-2xl{border-radius:1rem}
      .text-center{text-align:center}
      .bg-white{background:#fff}
      .shadow-md{box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)}
      .font-serif{font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif}
      .text-4xl{font-size:2rem}
      .text-6xl{font-size:3.5rem}
      .mt-4{margin-top:1rem}
      .mt-6{margin-top:1.5rem}
      .text-sm{font-size:.9rem}
      .btn{display:inline-block;padding:.5rem .75rem;border-radius:.5rem;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid transparent}
      .btn-primary{background:#7c3aed;color:#fff}
      .btn-ghost{background:transparent;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;color:#374151}
      .text-xs{font-size:.75rem;color:#6b7280}
    </style>
  </head>

  <body class="bg-violet-50 dark:bg-gray-900 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-10 shadow-md text-center">
        <div class="text-violet-600 dark:text-violet-300 font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold">
          400
        </div>
        <h2 class="mt-4 text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
          Permintaan Tidak Valid
        </h2>

        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Server tidak dapat memahami permintaan karena sintaks yang tidak valid.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Kembali ke Beranda</a>
          <a href="mailto:curatorian.id@gmail.com" class="btn">Laporkan jika perlu</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
